OL,3,CIs your heat pump tumble dryer a fire
OL,4,Crisk? How to check as 85,000 affected
OL,6,FWords by ITV News Producer Jamel Smith
OL,8,FTens of thousands of households with
OL,9,Fheat pump tumble dryers have been told
OL,10,Fto stop using their appliances over
OL,11,Ffire safety fears.
OL,13,FThe Office for Product Safety and
OL,14,FStandards (OPSS) warned on Thursday
OL,15,Fthat around 85,000 integrated heat
OL,16,Fpump tumble dryers made by the Chinese
OL,17,Fmultinational manufacturer Haier
OL,18,Fshould not be switched on.
