OL,3,CIs your heat pump tumble dryer a fire
OL,4,Crisk? How to check as 85,000 affected
OL,6,FBut what is the warning, and which
OL,7,Ftumble dryers are faulty? ITV News
OL,8,Fexplains.
OL,10,FWhat is the warning?
OL,12,FOPSS has said owners of some heat pump
OL,13,Ftumble dryers made by Haier should
OL,14,F"immediately" stop using them due to a
OL,15,Frisk that an internal short circuit
OL,16,Fcould overheat and cause a fire.
OL,18,FThis means that they fail to meet the
OL,19,Fsafety standards required for
OL,20,Felectronic goods.
