OL,6,FThe machines may not have come
OL,7,Fdirectly from Haier itself but from
OL,8,Fits subsidiaries like Candy or Iberna.
OL,10,FStop using the dryer immediately and
OL,11,Funplug it if possible to reduce the
OL,12,Frisk further, the OPSS said.
OL,14,FThen you should contact the
OL,15,Fmanufacturer to arrange a repair if
OL,16,Fyour model is listed.
OL,18,FWhat is a heat pump tumble dryer?
OL,20,FHeat pump tumble dryers are more
OL,21,Fenergy-efficient than regular dryers.
