OL,3,CIs your heat pump tumble dryer a fire
OL,4,Crisk? How to check as 85,000 affected
OL,6,FThey use a closed heat-exchange system
OL,7,Fto dry clothes at a lower temperature,
OL,8,Ftypically around 50C, compared with
OL,9,F70C to 75C for traditional models.
OL,11,FAlthough they take slightly longer to
OL,12,Fdry clothes, they use less energy and
OL,13,Fcan automatically switch off once the
OL,14,Flaundry is dry.
OL,16,FHas Haier already tried to repair the
OL,17,Fmachines?
