OL,6,FHaier began repairing 103,000 faulty
OL,7,Fdryers earlier this year but was
OL,8,Finstructed by the OPSS to pause after
OL,9,Fconcerns that the initial fix was
OL,10,Fstill unsafe.
OL,12,FAt the time, the National Fire Chiefs
OL,13,FCouncil and London Fire Brigade
OL,14,Fadvised owners to stop using them
OL,15,Funtil further checks were made.
OL,17,FFollowing an updated modification,
OL,18,FHaier has resumed its repair programme
OL,19,Fand started contacting consumers again.
