OL,6,FSue Davies, the head of Consumer
OL,7,FRights Policy at Which?, said people
OL,8,F"will understandably be worried" about
OL,9,Fthe fire safety fears.
OL,11,F"Although we are seeing an increase in
OL,12,Fthe number of households willing to
OL,13,Fconsider a heat pump, many remain
OL,14,Fconcerned about high upfront costs and
OL,15,Flack confidence that heat pumps will
OL,16,Freduce their energy bills and
OL,17,Feffectively heat their homes," she
OL,18,Fsaid in a statement on Thursday.
