OL,6,F"In order to support homeowners that
OL,7,Fare considering switching to a heat
OL,8,Fpump, the government needs to raise
OL,9,Fawareness about the grants, loans and
OL,10,Fcash back incentives that are
OL,11,Favailable, and ensure people have
OL,12,Faccess to good quality independent
OL,13,Fadvice and reliable installers."
OL,15,FWhat happens next?
OL,17,FHaier and OPSS say repairs will
OL,18,Fcontinue, and further guidance will be
OL,19,Fissued for customers with affected
OL,20,Fmachines.
